org.mapsforge.map.layer.renderer

Class DependencyCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapsforge.map.layer.renderer.DependencyCache

  • public class DependencyCache
extends Object
    This class process the methods for the Dependency Cache. It's connected with the LabelPlacement class. The main goal is, to remove double labels and symbols that are already rendered, from the actual object. Labels and symbols that, would be rendered on an already drawn Tile, will be deleted too.
